M|nate|| Stage | Benchmark | Drop-off to investigate |
M|nate||-------|-----------|------------------------|
M|nate|| Landing → Trial | > 12% | < 6% |
M|nate|| Trial → Activation (first sync) | > 70% | < 50% |
