M|nate|1. **Activation optimization** — getting users to their first transaction sync is the #1 lever; everything before paid conversion depends on this
M|nate|2. **K-factor / referral** — "Invite a colleague, both get 1 month free"; professional SaaS has high referral potential
M|nate|3. **LinkedIn organic** — thought leadership cnt from the founder increases trial sign-ups; target fin professionals
M|nate|4. **Trial email sequence** — 5-email onboarding: day 0 setup, day 1 first win, day 3 tip, day 7 check-in, day 14 upgrade nudge
M|nate|- If cohort Month 2 churn > 8%, the activation flow is the problem, not the product
M|nate|- Never recommend acquisition spend when activation rate is < 50%
